==Strength, casualties==

The following details have been given without a reference, and the source is suspect:<br /> 
Soviet commander=Gen. Maxim Hartsenko <br />
Axis strength=3 divisions: 45 000 , 83 tanks; casualties=6000 dead, 14 000 wounded, 400 lost, 21 tanks<br /> 
Soviet strength=2 divisions: 28 000, 140 tanks; casualties=4000 dead, 7500 wounded, 750 lost, 50 tanks.<br /> 
